        <rt-text data-qa="synopsis-value">Forced to retire after a goring, matador Diego Montez (Nacho Martínez) has since become a teacher. Among his students is Angel (Antonio Banderas), a naive boy so perversely desperate to impress that he attempts to rape Diego&#39;s girlfriend, Eva (Eva Cobo). He fails, but turns himself in regardless, also confessing to a series of murders he&#39;s recently seen in psychic visions. A lawyer (Assumpta Serna) steps in to defend him, but the police are unconvinced Angel is the real culprit.</rt-text>
